# Instrument Session Capture with a Change Ledger

## Step

Implement the capture contract from the [session-edge feasibility memo](../../../../joelclaw-wiki/.brain/session-edge-feasibility.svx) so sessionâ†’page change-edges become deterministically derivable:

- An append-only normalized change ledger emitted at capture time: sessionId, runtime, machineId, repo + worktree identity + starting HEAD, successful mutation tool calls with canonical repo-relative paths and pre/post blob hashes, worktree diffing for bulk shell/generator mutations (never parse command text), immutable `changeSetId`, commit-attribution events carrying `changeSetId` + contributing sessionIds + SHA, uncommitted/superseded markers, and amend/squash/rebase lineage.
